ceName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb12438">Adam, Robert</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02135">Schnitzler an Adam, 5. 5. 1913</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02137">Schnitzler an Adam, 13. 5. 1913</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02135">Schnitzler an Adam, 5. 5. 1913</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02137">Schnitzler an Adam, 13. 5. 1913</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
